This paper discusses the formulation and validation of RDF data, which involves database management (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for reasoning and mapping constraints to DL, machine learning (cs.LG) for identifying requirements and solutions, software engineering (cs.SE) for developing constraint languages, and programming languages (cs.PL) for formulating constraints.
